<td colspan="2" style="padding: 0px; padding-top: 2px; text-align:center; font-size:100%;" class=""><a href="/wiki/File:Yakof.jpg" class="image" title="Yakof.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f1/Yakof.jpg/180px-Yakof.jpg" width="180" height="148" border="0" /></a><br /></td>
